âœ… Output:

PowerShell logging demo started at 10/05/2025 19:00:01
2025-10-05T19:00:04.1234567Z - Log Entry #1
2025-10-05T19:00:07.1234567Z - Log Entry #2
...


Or run detached and watch logs:

